included.summary:
Professional with more than 4 years of experience; I have worked as an Interaction Designer, UX designer, HTML & CSS Designer or Front-End/Web UI Developer, I have helped to develop or design business intelligence, e-commerce, CRM, POS or administrative tools.

in this trajectory I have worked improving the UX/IxD from the different applications, worked with layouts and design, also worked with desktop applications or responsive applications,  doing, usability analysis, user research, need finding, prototyping, and user-centered design has been always present in the different processes.

Some of my tools have been HTML, CSS, Compass(SCSS), Bootstrap, Sketch, Invision, and other more.
